color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font></span><span
class=apple-style-span><font color=black face=Times><span style='font-family:
Times;color:black'>web-based technologies for resource interoperability,
inter-linkage, and access;</O:P></span></font></span><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><font size=3 color=black face=Symbol><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>&middot;</span></font><font
size=1 color=black><span style='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font><font
color=black face=Times><span style='font-family:Times;color:black'>multi-lingual
and/or multi-modal language resources, with focus on the mechanisms enabling
interoperability;<O:P></O:P></span></font><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><font size=3 color=black face=Symbol><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>&middot;</span></font><font
size=1 color=black><span style='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font><font
color=black face=Times><span style='font-family:Times;color:black'>support for
multi-linguality and multi-modality in systems/frameworks for resource
creation, annotation,&nbsp;&nbsp;use, and access;<O:P></O:P></span></font><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><font size=3 color=black face=Symbol><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>&middot;</span></font><font
size=1 color=black><span style='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font><font
color=black face=Times><span style='font-family:Times;color:black'>existing and
proposed standards for language resources, including standards for linguistic
annotations at any and all linguistics levels;<O:P></O:P></span></font><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><font size=3 color=black face=Symbol><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>&middot;</span></font><font
size=1 color=black><span style='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font><font
color=black face=Times><span style='font-family:Times;color:black'>systems,
frameworks, and architectures to support the development and use of
interoperable language resources;<O:P></O:P></span></font><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><font size=3 color=black face=Symbol><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>&middot;</span></font><font
size=1 color=black><span style='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font><font
color=black face=Times><span style='font-family:Times;color:black'>evaluation
of existing resources, systems and frameworks, and/or standards in terms of
support for interoperability;<O:P></O:P></span></font><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><font size=3 color=black face=Symbol><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>&middot;</span></font><font
size=1 color=black><span style='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font><font
color=black face=Times><span style='font-family:Times;color:black'>harmonization,
integration, and/or linking of language resources, including corpora, wordnets,
framenets, ontologies, etc.;<O:P></O:P></span></font><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt'><font size=3 color=black face=Symbol><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>&middot;</span></font><font
size=1 color=black><span style='font-size:7.0pt;color:black'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font><font
color=black face=Times><span style='font-family:Times;color:black'>ontologies
for language resources, especially for support of&nbsp;&nbsp;multi-linguality,
multi-culturality, and multi-modality.&nbsp;</span></font><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto'><b><font
size=3 color=black face=Times><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Times;
color:black;font-weight:bold'>Proceedings<O:P></O:P></span></font></b><o:p></o:p></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto'><font
